OL,6,FA prisoner who strangled his cellmate
OL,7,Fto death using a TV aerial cord before
OL,8,Fattacking his former cellmate in the
OL,9,Fshowers has been sentenced.
OL,11,FMichael Harkin killed Dan Childs and
OL,12,Fwounded a second prisoner at HMP
OL,13,FBristol in June last year.
OL,15,FThe 35-year-old, who has
OL,16,Fschizophrenia, was cleared of murder
OL,17,Fby a jury in July but found guilty of
OL,18,Fmanslaughter on grounds of diminished
OL,19,Fresponsibility.
