OL,6,FHe was also found guilty of wounding
OL,7,Fanother prisoner but cleared of one
OL,8,Fcharge of attempting to wound a member
OL,9,Fof prison staff.
OL,11,FHarkin was handed an indefinite
OL,12,Fhospital order at a sentencing hearing
OL,13,Fat Bristol Crown Court on 11 October.
OL,15,FThe court heard Harkin strangled Mr
OL,16,FChilds, who was 38, before leaving him
OL,17,F"tucked up" in sheets on the top bunk
OL,18,Fon 5 June last year.
