OL,6,FIt was only when police were called to
OL,7,Fthis assault that Mr Childs was
OL,8,Fdiscovered unresponsive in his cell.
OL,9,FHe died at the scene.
OL,11,FSpeaking after Harkins was convicted,
OL,12,FSenior Investigating Officer for Avon
OL,13,Fand Somerset Police DI Nadine
OL,14,FPartridge said: "Our thoughts are
OL,15,Fforemost with the family of Dan
OL,16,FChilds, who have had their much-loved
OL,17,Fson, brother and uncle taken away from
OL,18,Fthem.
