OL,6,F"A specially-trained officer continues
OL,7,Fto provide them with support at what
OL,8,Fcontinues to be an incredibly
OL,9,Fdifficult time for them.
OL,11,F"Harkin has been remanded ahead of a
OL,12,Fsentencing hearing later in the year,
OL,13,Ffollowing the completion of
OL,14,Fpsychiatric reports".
